also -- philosophy, economics --

00:05:11.860 --> 00:05:14.890
working on both the empirical
and the moral dimensions

00:05:14.890 --> 00:05:15.910
of these questions.

00:05:15.910 --> 00:05:20.220
And I look forward to,
you know, doing more.

